chatclient

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • chatclient.Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientCallback, java.rmi.Remote

    public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClientCallback
    A class to instantiate a client for the chat server. Any number of clients can exist simultanously. Its interactions with the chat server are described at the package level.
